WEBVTT

00:02:27.520 --> 00:02:31.000
and it's the same gap
that existed a decade earlier.

00:02:32.000 --> 00:02:34.296
And it really is a shame,

00:02:34.320 --> 00:02:39.336
because I am so convinced that the world
is in real need for women leaders

00:02:39.360 --> 00:02:41.416
and more principle-based leadership

00:02:41.440 --> 00:02:42.640
in general.

00:02:44.080 --> 00:02:46.600
So my decision to run

00:02:47.680 --> 00:02:51.136
ultimately came down to the fact

00:02:51.160 --> 00:02:52.360
that I felt

00:02:53.360 --> 00:02:55.640
that I had to do my bit,

00:02:57.640 --> 00:03:00.040
even if I had no political experience,